title: Great App!
comment: I love this app and use it during the work day almost every day. I'm sure my data provider hates me.  The big flaw with this app is that the search feature is greatly limited. It could be a little less cumbersome. All the filters work great but when you go "back" out of the search it brings you to the home screen whereras I think it would be better if the "back" button would bring the user back to the previous search results. Also, bookmarking doesn't work too well. When search results are showing and a show is long pressed the bookmark feature is one of the selections but doesn't put the show into bookmarks, aka favorites. The only way to bookmark is to actually go to the song listing in each show and tapping the star so when you go back, you're brought back to the home screen.  Otherwise, thanks for this great app.
